Class NodeFilter_Downsample

  • java.lang.Object
    • filters.NodeFilter_Downsample
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INodeFilter

    public class NodeFilter_Downsample
extends Object
implements INodeFilter
    Filter which reduces the number of nodes in a list. Usually done for visualization or computational reasons. Only applies to lists of nodes. Single node evaluations will always return true.

    matt
